The paper deals with image classification tasks, specifically face verification and object recognition, which are typically categorized under computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed model is based on deep learning, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The model is evaluated on datasets, which involves multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, and cs.IR.
